Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.07,0:38:10.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,我总是觉得茫茫宇宙中有些神秘的和谐\N{\rENG}I've always felt there was some kind of mystical core to the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.57,0:38:15.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,最近我在想有关我啊，我的性格之类的\N{\rENG}But, more recently, I've started to think that, me, my personality, whatever...
