Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.05,0:38:24.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我越想到这个，就越觉得不能浪费人生\N{\rENG}And the more I think that, I can't go through life saying this is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.05,0:38:28.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为生命仅此一次，任何事情，不管是有趣的\N{\rENG}This is it. This is actually happening.What do you think is interesting?
