Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.23,0:38:43.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,“你还好吧”“你不会得了癌症吧？你会去自杀吗？”\N{\rENG}"Are you okay? Do you have cancer?Are you gonna commit suicide? "
